      <title>HiveSQL | Date</title>
      <link href="/HiveSQL-Date.html"/>
      <url>/HiveSQL-Date.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>约定：<br><code>date</code>：<code>yyyyMMdd</code>格式的日期<br><code>date_</code>：<code>yyyy-MM-dd</code>格式的日期<br><code>ts</code>：时间戳</p></blockquote><h2 id="基本语法"><a href="#基本语法" class="headerlink" title="基本语法"></a>基本语法</h2><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">----- 周几/星期几 -----</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 取值范围1-7</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cast</span>(date_format(date_, <span class="string">&#x27;u&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> <span class="type">int</span>)  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 取值范围0-6</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cast</span>(pmod(datediff(date_, <span class="string">&#x27;1900-01-07&#x27;</span>), <span class="number">7</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="格式转换"><a href="#格式转换" class="headerlink" title="格式转换"></a>格式转换</h2><h3 id="日期-与-日期"><a href="#日期-与-日期" class="headerlink" title="日期 与 日期"></a>日期 与 日期</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- yyyyMMdd 转 yyyy-MM-dd</span></span><br><span class="line">to_date(<span class="type">date</span>)</span><br><span class="line">from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(<span class="type">date</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyyMMdd&#x27;</span>), <span class="string">&#x27;yyyy-MM-dd&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- yyyy-MM-dd 转 yyyyMMdd</span></span><br><span class="line">from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(date_, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyy-MM-dd&#x27;</span>), <span class="string">&#x27;yyyyMMdd&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="日期-与-时间戳"><a href="#日期-与-时间戳" class="headerlink" title="日期 与 时间戳"></a>日期 与 时间戳</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 10位时间戳(bigint格式，单位秒) 转 日期yyyyMMdd</span></span><br><span class="line">from_unixtime(ts, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyyMMdd&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 13位时间戳（单位毫秒） 转 yyyyMMdd</span></span><br><span class="line">from_unixtime(ts <span class="operator">/</span> <span class="number">1000</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyyMMdd&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 10位时间戳（bigint格式，单位秒） 转 日期yyyy-MM-dd</span></span><br><span class="line">from_unixtime(ts, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyy-MM-dd&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 10位时间戳（bigint格式，单位秒） 转 yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss</span></span><br><span class="line">from_unixtime(ts, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="时间戳-与-时间戳"><a href="#时间戳-与-时间戳" class="headerlink" title="时间戳 与 时间戳"></a>时间戳 与 时间戳</h3><h2 id="常用日期"><a href="#常用日期" class="headerlink" title="常用日期"></a>常用日期</h2><h3 id="周度"><a href="#周度" class="headerlink" title="周度"></a>周度</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- （往前）最近一个周日</span></span><br><span class="line">date_sub(<span class="built_in">current_date</span>, <span class="built_in">cast</span>(date_format(<span class="built_in">current_date</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;u&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> <span class="type">int</span>))</span><br><span class="line">date_sub(<span class="type">date</span>, pmod(datediff(<span class="type">date</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2001-01-07&#x27;</span>), <span class="number">7</span>))</span><br><span class="line">date_sub(<span class="type">date</span>, datediff(<span class="type">date</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2001-01-07&#x27;</span>) <span class="operator">%</span> <span class="number">7</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- （往前）最近一个周六</span></span><br><span class="line">date_sub(<span class="type">date</span>, pmod(datediff(<span class="type">date</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2001-01-06&#x27;</span>), <span class="number">7</span>))</span><br><span class="line">date_sub(<span class="type">date</span>, datediff(<span class="type">date</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2001-01-06&#x27;</span>) <span class="operator">%</span> <span class="number">7</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- （往前）当周的周一</span></span><br><span class="line">date_sub(<span class="built_in">current_date</span>, <span class="built_in">cast</span>(date_format(<span class="built_in">current_date</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;u&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> <span class="type">int</span>) <span class="operator">-</span> <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- （往后）最近一个周一</span></span><br><span class="line">date_add(<span class="type">date</span>, <span class="number">6</span> <span class="operator">-</span> pmod(datediff(<span class="type">date</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2001-01-02&#x27;</span>), <span class="number">7</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- （往后）最近一个周二</span></span><br><span class="line">date_add(<span class="type">date</span>, <span class="number">6</span> <span class="operator">-</span> pmod(datediff(<span class="type">date</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2001-01-03&#x27;</span>), <span class="number">7</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- （往后）最近一个周日</span></span><br><span class="line">date_add(<span class="type">date</span>, <span class="number">6</span> <span class="operator">-</span> pmod(datediff(<span class="type">date</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2001-01-01&#x27;</span>), <span class="number">7</span>))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 2001-01-01 周一</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 2001-01-07 周日</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="月度"><a href="#月度" class="headerlink" title="月度"></a>月度</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 取当前每月最后一天（不一定是月末最后一天）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> </span><br><span class="line">(</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">case</span>    <span class="keyword">when</span> <span class="string">&#x27;$&#123;date&#125;&#x27;</span> <span class="operator">=</span> last_day(<span class="string">&#x27;$&#123;date&#125;&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="type">date</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;$&#123;date&#125;&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">then</span> <span class="number">1</span> </span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">when</span> <span class="string">&#x27;$&#123;date&#125;&#x27;</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span> last_day(<span class="string">&#x27;$&#123;date&#125;&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="type">date</span> <span class="operator">=</span> last_day(add_months(<span class="string">&#x27;$&#123;date&#125;&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">-1</span>)) <span class="keyword">then</span> <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line">) <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- n月前同一天</span></span><br><span class="line">add_months(<span class="built_in">current_date</span>, <span class="operator">-</span>n)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 当月第一天</span></span><br><span class="line">date_format(<span class="built_in">current_date</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyy-MM-01&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 当月最后一天</span></span><br><span class="line">last_day(<span class="built_in">current_date</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- n月前最后一天</span></span><br><span class="line">last_day(add_months(<span class="type">date</span>, <span class="operator">-</span>n))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 上个月最后一天</span></span><br><span class="line">last_day(add_months(<span class="type">date</span>, <span class="number">-1</span>))</span><br><span class="line">date_sub(date_format(<span class="built_in">current_date</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyy-MM-01&#x27;</span>), <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Reference"><a href="#Reference" class="headerlink" title="Reference"></a>Reference</h2>]]></content>
      
      
